                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for hydrogen-based low-carbon smelting of ferronickel from laterite-nickel ore",
                    "一种红土镍矿氢基低碳冶炼镍铁的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a laterite-nickel ore hydrogen-based low-carbon ferronickel smelting method which comprises the following steps: (1) mixing dried, crushed and ground laterite-nickel ore powder with a composite binder and slaked lime according to a certain proportion, and pelletizing in a disc pelletizer to obtain green pellets; (2) drying and roasting the green pellets prepared in the step (1) to prepare oxidizing pellets; (3) in a hydrogen-rich reduction shaft furnace, reducing the oxidized pellets at a certain temperature to obtain nickel-containing direct reduced iron (DRI); (4) cooling the nickel-containing DRI to below 50 DEG C under the protection of inert gas, and then crushing, ball-milling and magnetically separating to obtain a ferronickel product; and (5) carrying out briquetting and electric heating melting separation on the magnetically separated ferro-nickel product to obtain the ferro-nickel alloy."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开一种红土镍矿氢基低碳冶炼镍铁的方法，包括以下步骤：（1）将经干燥、破碎、研磨过的红土镍矿粉与复合粘结剂、消石灰按照一定比例混料，然后进入圆盘造球机进行造球，制得生球；（2）将步骤（1）制备的生球进行干燥与焙烧，制备氧化性球团；（3）在富氢还原竖炉中、一定温度下将氧化球团还原得到含镍直接还原铁（DRI）；（4）将含镍DRI在惰性气体保护下冷却至50℃以下后经破碎、球磨、磁选后得到镍铁产物；（5）将磁选后镍铁产物进行压块及电热熔分，获得镍铁合金。"
                }
            ]
